title: Hillary Clinton shines in Democratic debate — with Bernie Sanders’ help
text: Hillary Clinton reminded voters Tuesday — in case any of them had forgotten — why she is the frontrunner for the Democratic presidential nomination. Clinton delivered a more polished and robust performance in the first 2016 primary debate
